modName: Mileena Nord Preset for ECE And Racemenu
summary: A save slot for ECE and Racemenu
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/2B7vB2d.jpg[/img][/center]

*Edit : Added another file for Racemenu :)
I decided to share my CME save, to use it you will need to have [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]ECE[/url] OR [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu[/url] And [url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url].
there is a Readme file included that will have basic instructions on how to install it.

The following files are[color=#ff0000] [/color][u][color=#ffff00]required [/color][/u]to make your character look like in my screenshots:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?]UNP BLESSED BODY -UNPB[/url] by [b]Blessed Redux Project team
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url] by [b]Hello Santa[/b][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] by [b]HHaleyy (INSTALL [color=#ffff00]AFTER [/color]SG Female Textures)[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]  by [b]Gabriel Mailhot[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url]  by [b]Hello Santa[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url] by [b]Hvergelmir[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair[/url] by [b]Apachii[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?]XP32 Maximum Skeleton -XPMS[/url] by [b]xp32[/b]

Armors in my screenshots (Recommended):
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53442/?]zzjay's wardrobe[/url] by [b]zzjay[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59399/?]Crimson Twilight Armor[/url] by [b]BloodFree[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60389/?]Crimson Twilight - Al Dahna Re-Tex[/url] by [b]betterbecause[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61546/?]Vampire Rogue Armor[/url] by [b]TheBlitz77[/b]

The ENB i'm using is Snapdragon ENB (not on the nexus, google it!)
Hopefully that was everything. If I've forgotten something, let me know in the comments, feel free to ask anything. :)
[color=#00ff00]Please don't forget to Endorse.[/color]
